reviews.review_description:
I live in Australia, and unfortunately at the moment there are no Oceanic servers so in best case scenario I have 350ms ping. I also have frequent issues with the in game voice chat where my friend and I were unable to hear each other without doing a full restart.

This game is fun as hell, it’s a great laugh and I got a few great hours out of it. I understand this game is in early access so to conclude my review;

If this game had Oceanic servers and the in game voice chat was fixed I would pay triple the asking price. It truly is so much fun. I can’t wait to see how this game develops in the future.
